      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"rest\" thing sounds nice but it's not really helping. It's more like... if I just stopped trying, it would actually be a relief. Everything feels so pointless. I do the same things every day, see the same streets, but nobody actually sees me. I'm basically a zero in a world of numbers.",
